title: 49 - Nicole Aimee Schreiber
itunes:title: 49 - Nicole Aimee Schreiber
description: Most Americans have three names, but very few of us have the jimmy-jacks to use all three. Nicole clearly gives -3 fucks. She’s a wonderful writer and comedian based in LA. We met her while Sean was performing with her at the Comedy Cellar in Vegas. She has opened for Dave Attel, toured with Bobby Lee, and is a paid regular at the world famous Comedy Store (Happy 48th anniversary, by the way)! Here are five words to describe this episode: never trust rich people’s parents.
